      <img src="images/multiproject/01-project.png"/>
      </p>
      <p>
      You mat create the maven project files manually, or press the <img src="/org/jbundle/res/images/buttons/Run.gif"/> 'Create maven projects' button to create
      a skeleton project file in each of the project directories and in the parent directory.
      </p>
